      "pos": [
        8088,
        8176
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Locate the pfup_pfwssdk_PfWsSdk setting and change the value from “http://localhost:4898/PfWsSdk.asmx” to the URL of the Web Service SDK that is running on the Azure Multi-Factor Authentication Server (e.g. https://computer1.domain.local/MultiFactorAuthWebServiceSdk/PfWsSdk.asmx).",
      "pos": [
        8180,
        8461
